Package: chromHMMviewR
Type: Package
Title: Visualize ChromHMM Outputs In R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Adrià Mitjavila Ventura
Maintainer: Adrià Mitjavila Ventura <adria.mitjavila94@gmail.com>
Description: chromHMMviewR takes the output files from ChromHMM LearnModel and draws a 
